{"tid":1598644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小心護旗手影相篤灰","createTime":"2019-09-27T14:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T15:05:54.000Z","uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"30a37182d458dbbb7118c73a236c53cc5f86069b","tid":1598644,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:38:35.000Z","msg":"【有團體成立義工隊守護國旗　強調不會武力護旗】<br />\n<br />\n守護香港大聯盟發起「全民護旗行動」，呼籲市民在國慶期間共同守護國旗，包括成立國慶護旗義工隊，預計有過萬人參與。<br />\n<br />\n聯盟召集人黃英豪表示，護旗隊會分成港島、九龍、新界東及新界北四個區，強調護旗隊不會挑起爭端及不會以武力護旗，而會勸喻違法者及報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #港台電視31 #港台電視32 #十點半新聞天地 #守護香港大聯盟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小心班扑街影相篤灰，發現時要即時制止"},{"pid":"2c1f9c67b10636907fad1a0ee5580846269f4b4a","tid":1598644,"uid":210254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:45:35.000Z","msg":"預計有過萬人參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e74980d0faf75b3c8ecb164149242c65bf7382","tid":1598644,"uid":46148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:48:23.000Z","msg":"神獸召喚"},{"pid":"98c5f0b1c7eb7d1c2e3c7a10134b9e04df394f21","tid":1598644,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:48:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"138414c78899fffe4ab33ee71af87fc86733b910","tid":1598644,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87e74980d0faf75b3c8ecb164149242c65bf7382","tid":1598644,"uid":46148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:48:23.000Z","msg":"神獸召喚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:51:52.000Z","msg":"啱，最少要用神獸吞噬相機"},{"pid":"8665711758e0a5ac9785ebe85d9a0feeb21a99f2","tid":1598644,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:56:30.000Z","msg":"小心喬裝護旗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67ffb49023e972d277e28ea05654e18fd8f4bfb","tid":1598644,"uid":320978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T15:04:07.000Z","msg":"係唔係要